    <h3>Zero JavaScript</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-content">
    <p>
      By default, Astro ships <strong>zero client-side JavaScript</strong>. 
      This component is pure HTML/CSS, rendering instantly on the server.
    </p>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="value">100%</span>
      <span class="label">Static HTML</span>
    </div>
